\c 3
\s Ukubizwa kukaMozisi
\p
\v 1 UMozisi wayeselusa-ke umhlambi kaJetro uyisezala, umpristi weMidiyani; waqhuba umhlambi waya ngaphambili kwenkangala\x + Hlab. 139.9.\x* waze wafika entabeni kaNkulunkulu\x + 4.27; 18.5; 24.13. Nani 10.33. 1 Kho. 19.8.\x*, eHorebe.
\v 2 Njalo ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yabonakala kuye\x + Isa. 63.9. Mal. 3.1. Seb. 7.30,31. Gen. 18.2.\x* elangabini lomlilo liphuma phakathi kwesihlahla\x + Dute. 33.16.\x*; wasebona, khangela-ke, isihlahla sivutha umlilo, kodwa isihlahla sasingapheli.
\v 3 UMozisi wasesithi: Ngizaphambuka-ke ngibone lo umbono omkhulu, ukuthi kungani isihlahla singatshi.
\v 4 Kwathi iN\nd kosi\nd* isibonile ukuthi uphambukile ukuyabona, uNkulunkulu wambiza ephakathi kwesihlahla, wathi: Mozisi, Mozisi! Wasesithi: Khangela ngi\add lapha\add*.
\v 5 Wasesithi: Ungasondeli lapha; khupha amanyathela akho enyaweni zakho, ngoba indawo omi kuyo ingumhlabathi ongcwele\x + Josh. 5.15. Seb. 7.33.\x*.
\v 6 Wathi futhi: NginguNkulunkulu kayihlo, uNkulunkulu kaAbrahama, uNkulunkulu kaIsaka, loNkulunkulu kaJakobe\x + Gen. 28.13. 3.15; 4.5. Seb. 7.32. Mat. 22.32. Mark. 12.26. Luka 20.37.\x*. UMozisi wasefihla ubuso bakhe, ngoba esesaba ukukhangela uNkulunkulu\x + 1 Kho. 19.13. Isa. 6.1,2,5.\x*.
\p
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Isibili ngibonile ukuhlupheka kwesizwe sami esiseGibhithe\x + 2.23,24,25. Neh. 9.9. Hlab. 106.44. Seb. 7.34.\x*, ngizwile ukukhala kwabo ngenxa yabaqhubi besibhalo babo\x + 5.6,10,13,14.\x*; ngoba ngiyazazi insizi zabo;
\v 8 njalo ngehlile\x + Gen. 11.5,7; 18.21.\x* ukusikhulula ezandleni zamaGibhithe\x + 6.6.\x*, lokusenyusa kulelolizwe, ngisise elizweni elihle elibanzi\x + Dute. 1.25; 8.7,8,9.\x*, siye elizweni eligeleza uchago loluju\x + 3.17; 13.5; 33.3. Levi 20.24. Nani 13.27. Dute. 26.9,15. Jer. 11.5; 32.22. Hez. 20.6.\x*, siye endaweni yamaKhanani lamaHethi lamaAmori lamaPerizi lamaHivi lamaJebusi\x + Gen. 15.18-21.\x*.
\v 9 Khathesi-ke, khangela, ukukhala kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli sekufikile kimi\x + 2.23.\x*; njalo lami ngibonile ucindezelo amaGibhithe abacindezela ngalo.
\v 10 Khathesi-ke, woza, ngizakuthuma kuFaro ukuze ukhuphe isizwe sami, abantwana bakoIsrayeli, eGibhithe.
\p
\v 11 Kodwa uMozisi wathi kuNkulunkulu: Ngingubani mina\x + 1 Sam. 18.18. 6.12. Jer. 1.6.\x* ukuthi ngiye kuFaro, lokuthi ngikhuphe abantwana bakoIsrayeli eGibhithe?
\v 12 Wasesithi: Isibili ngizakuba lawe\x + Gen. 31.3. Dute. 31.8,23. Josh. 1.5.\x*; lalokhu kuzakuba yisibonakaliso kuwe sokuthi mina ngikuthumile; lapho ususikhuphile isizwe eGibhithe, lizamkhonza uNkulunkulu kulintaba\x + 19.3-5.\x*.
\v 13 UMozisi wasesithi kuNkulunkulu: Khangela, nxa ngifika kubantwana bakoIsrayeli ngisithi kubo: UNkulunkulu waboyihlo ungithumile kini; bazakuthi kimi: Ungubani ibizo lakhe? Ngizathini kubo?
\v 14 UNkulunkulu wasesithi kuMozisi: NGINGUYE ENGINGUYE. Wathi futhi: Uzakutsho njalo kubantwana bakoIsrayeli \add ukuthi\add*: UNGINGUYE\x + 6.3. Joha. 8.58. Heb. 13.8. Isam. 1.4; 4.8.\x* ungithumile kini.
\v 15 UNkulunkulu wasesithi njalo kuMozisi: Uzakutsho njalo kubantwana bakoIsrayeli ukuthi: IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyihlo, uNkulunkulu kaAbrahama, uNkulunkulu kaIsaka, loNkulunkulu kaJakobe\x + 3.6.\x* ungithumile kini; leli libizo lami kuze kube nininini\x + Hos. 12.5. Hlab. 135.13.\x*, njalo lesi yisikhumbuzo sami kusizukulwana kusiya kusizukulwana.
\v 16 Hamba, ubuthanise abadala bakoIsrayeli\x + 4.29.\x*, uthi kubo: IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyihlo ibonakele kimi, uNkulunkulu kaAbrahama, kaIsaka, lokaJakobe, isithi: Ngokulihambela ngilihambele\x + Gen. 50.24. Eks. 4.31. Luka 1.68.\x*, lalokho elikwenziwe eGibhithe;
\v 17 futhi ngathi ngizalenyusa enhluphekweni yeGibhithe, ngilise elizweni lamaKhanani lelamaHethi lelamaAmori lelamaPerizi lelamaHivi lelamaJebusi\x + 3.8.\x*, liye elizweni eligeleza uchago loluju.
\v 18 Njalo bazalalela ilizwi lakho\x + 4.31.\x*. Futhi uzakuya, wena\x + 5.1.\x* labadala bakoIsrayeli, enkosini yeGibhithe, lithi kuyo: IN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamaHebheru, ihlangene lathi\x + Nani 23.3,4,15,16.\x*; khathesi-ke, ake usiyekele sihambe ummango wensuku ezintathu siye enkangala ukuze sihlabele iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu.
\v 19 Kodwa mina ngiyazi ukuthi inkosi yeGibhithe kayiyikuliyekela lihambe\x + 5.2; 7.4.\x*, ngitsho langesandla esilamandla.
\v 20 Ngakho ngizakwelula isandla sami\x + 7.1-13.21. Seb. 7.36.\x* ngilitshaye iGibhithe ngezimangaliso zami zonke engizazenza phakathi kwalo; njalo emva kwalokho izaliyekela lihambe\x + 12.31.\x*.
\v 21 Njalo ngizanika lesisizwe umusa emehlweni amaGibhithe\x + Gen. 15.14. Eks. 11.2,3; 12.35,36.\x*. Kuzakuthi-ke mhla lisukayo, kaliyikusuka lingelalutho,
\v 22 kodwa \add wonke\add* owesifazana uzacela kumakhelwane wakhe, lakuye ohlezihleziyo endlini yakhe, izinto zesiliva, lezinto zegolide, lemvunulo; lizazifaka emadodaneni enu lemadodakazini enu; lizawaphanga\x + Eks. 33.6. 2 Lan. 20.25.\x* amaGibhithe\f + \fk amaGibhithe: \fl kumbe, \fq iGibhithe.\f*.
